            <p class="text-center">
                Having issues with the design or implementation aspects of a project? Recruit my team to remedy the situation!
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <a asp-page="./SpecificService" asp-route-postId="1"><button class="btn btn-primary w-100">LEARN MORE</button></a>
